CSS - Cascading Style Sheets
for OK | Cancel button independent to OS -> Button Box

Useful widgets:
qTool Button -> Use it instead of the simple Push Button
qTab Widget -> elegant and useful

for CSS style -> Properties of Widget -> Style Sheets
surround the CSS style with QName_of_Widget{} to implement it to the current widget only

classic example for CSS styling:

QFrame{
background-color: qradialgradient(spread:repeat, cx:0.5, cy:0.5, radius:0.077, fx:0.5, fy:0.5, stop:0 rgba(0, 169, 255, 147), stop:0.497326 rgba(0, 0, 0, 147), stop:1 rgba(0, 169, 255, 147));
}

QToolButton {
background-color : transparent;
border : none;
}

QToolButton:checked {
background-color:rgb[193, 210, 238];
}
